title: Dog and Beth On The Hunt S02E05 WS DSR x264-NY2 mp4
description:
The Long Arm of the Dog - Veteran Alabama bondsman Gage Huffstetler of Fast Feet Bail Bonds reaches out to Dog and Beth with an emergency. She has a jump that has run to California, and the court has suspended her bail license until she brings him in. Can Dog and Beth help Gage catch her fugitive and get the business back on track?
